    "Id": "chassisdef_ranger_RGR-3X",
    "Name": "Ranger",
    "Details": "Introduced in 3112 following Firefly Foundry's partnership with Clan Sea Fox, the RGR-3X blends Inner Sphere and Clan technology into an all-energy configuration. A center-torso Angel ECM Suite provides electronic warfare capability absent from earlier variants. The left arm mounts a standard ER PPC for long-range fire, while two right-arm Clan Improved Heavy Medium Lasers and a left-arm Improved Heavy Small Laser deliver devastating close-range damage output. Eighteen Double Heat Sinks manage the considerable heat load.\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Quirk: Accurate Weapon - Energy</color></b>\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Drop Cost Multiplier: 1.05</color></b>",
    "Icon": "uixTxrIcon_ranger3x"
