  "StockRole": "Skirmisher",
  "YangsThoughts": "The Ranger was one of Firefly Foundry's first two designs, built for both internal use and export, and it sold broadly across the Periphery and eventually into the AFFS as well. It is a dependable medium frame rather than a flashy one, the kind of workhorse that keeps a unit functional when more exotic hardware is in the shop. Later variants integrated Clan Sea Fox technology, which pushed the ceiling considerably beyond what the original design suggested was possible.",
